<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Compared with platforms that require more manual configuration, MoneyFlare markets itself as a more automated AI trading option. Users can activate available strategies, while the platform handles certain execution and management functions automatically.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This may appeal to users interested in automated crypto investing with lower day-to-day involvement.</span></p>
