<h3><b>Beginner tip</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Monitor spreads regularly, as arbitrage opportunities can change quickly.</span></p>
<h2><b>7. Coinrule — No-Code Crypto Trading Bot</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Coinrule is a no-code crypto trading bot platform that allows users to create strategies using simple rules.</span></p>
